OL,3,CReports of abuse against road workers
OL,4,Creaches new high in Southampton
OL,6,FThe amount of roadworks has gone up by
OL,7,Fat least 10% over the last five years.
OL,8,FBut what's also soared is the level of
OL,9,Fabuse aimed at roadworkers.
OL,11,FIn Southampton, half of staff say
OL,12,Fthey've experienced abuse ranging from
OL,13,Fverbal - to physical - and it can
OL,14,Fhappen a number of times a day.
OL,16,FSome workers have reported being
OL,17,Fphysically threatened and having
OL,18,Fobjects thrown at them such as
OL,19,Fbarriers and traffic cones.
